TABLE
    TROW
        TCELL "50%"
            DIV "card"
                DIV "card-body"
                    IMAGE "/kytschi/imgs/portfolio/kytschbasic.png", "kytschBASIC"
                DIV CLOSE
                DIV "card-footer"
                    SWRITE
                        PRINT "kytschBASIC"
                    SWRITE CLOSE
                DIV CLOSE
            DIV CLOSE
        TCELL CLOSE
        TCELL ,"table-text-right"
            SWRITE
                PRINT "A web language that is better than anything that currently exists! I should know, I wrote it!"
            SWRITE CLOSE
            SWRITE
                PRINT "What is kytschBASIC?", "text-heading"
            SWRITE CLOSE
            SWRITE
                PRINT "kytschBASIC come from an idea I had when reading one of my AmigaBASIC books. I thought "wouldn't it be cool to have a version of BASIC that rendered modern day websites" and so I set out to make it possible."
            SWRITE CLOSE
            SWRITE
                PRINT "The first build I did in c++ but I just wasn't happy with the library that I was using for serving the HTML. Don't get me wrong its a good library but it just didn't fit what I was after. I'd seen zephir-lang which lets you build PHP modules and it was something I was keen to play with so I began the port over to zephir."
            SWRITE CLOSE
            SWRITE
                PRINT "So to sum up...kytschBASIC lets you write in a version of BASIC that is heavily inspired by AmigaBASIC and it'll render that code as HTML and CSS so it can be viewed via the web. It has support for jQuery also so you can do javascript integration."
            SWRITE CLOSE
        TCELL CLOSE
    TROW CLOSE
    TROW
        TCELL "50%","table-text"
            SWRITE
                PRINT "Want to check it out and get involved, click below..."
                LINE BREAK
                LINE BREAK
                LINK "https://github.com/kytschi/kytschBASIC", "Check the repo out", "nav-link-img", "_blank"
                    IMAGE "/kytschi/imgs/noclick.gif", "Take me to the repo"
                LINK CLOSE
            SWRITE CLOSE
        TCELL CLOSE
        TCELL
            IMAGE "/kytschi/imgs/arrow.png", "arrow", "arrow-small"
        TCELL CLOSE
    TROW CLOSE
TABLE CLOSE
